  "$comment": "Refined tokens for Korbey Lague PLLP. Changes from the original brief are minimal and conservative — palette hexes are untouched (brand). Refinements: (1) heading weights 600/800 added to the font import so headings can go heavier for a sharper, more modern voice; (2) radius scale tightened (lg 16px → 6px) to honor the 'sharp' shape system — the original 16px lg read too soft for a modern advisory firm; (3) near-black deepened slightly and given a hair less blue for cleaner body ink. Everything else matches the brief. See design-overrides.css for all expressive styling.",

